l respond to resigning members. Two Beer Can and two 4S", "events were successful and should start in May.", "g. Port Committee (Bob Bush): Nothing to report.", "h. Race Committee (Scott Barrar): Race schedule will track last year\u2019s schedule.", "i. Social Committee (Amanda McCullum): Feb 16th is the Chili Cook-off at 4:00 pm.", "Condiments are provided and some beer provided. St. Patrick\u2019s Day, Amanda is", "looking for two volunteers to host the event on March 15th.", "j. Information Officer (Ed Bourguignon): Ed wants to send newsletter, send him", "information if you want it included. Willamette holding a race management clinic", "on March 14th.", "k. Sailing School (_____): Not present.", "2"], "bbox": [[0.176634, 0.05624, 0.138722, 0.015516], [0.147222, 0.058396, 0.013667999999999986, 0.013889], [0.176634, 0.084523, 0.6740759999999999, 0.015516], [0.176634, 0.102073, 0.06592500000000001, 0.015516], [0.176634, 0.129725, 0.5292730000000001, 0.015516], [0.147222, 0.157376, 0.27132199999999995, 0.015516], [0.176634, 0.192477, 0.37541700000000006, 0.015516], [0.147222, 0.220129, 0.21747000000000002, 0.015516], [0.176634, 0.24778, 0.07979999999999998, 0.015516], [0.147222, 0.282881, 0.359391, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.317982, 0.63669, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.335993, 0.39934600000000003, 0.015814], [0.206046, 0.372907, 0.5873349999999999, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.409523, 0.6700679999999999, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.444624, 0.6652750000000001, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.460533, 0.6342999999999999, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.476568, 0.23372900000000002, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.515836, 0.6601889999999999, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.533386, 0.5212379999999999, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.568487, 0.6758979999999999, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.586038, 0.6096189999999999, 0.015516], [0.235458, 0.603588, 0.380215, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.638689, 0.40285199999999993, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.675306, 0.6517710000000001, 0.015516], [0.206046, 0.71175, 0.673996, 0.015688], [0.235458, 0.73023,